{"tid":384603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［人唔笑］曾鈺成講國歌法：要對政府、立會有信心　不存在不覺意違法","createTime":"2017-09-02T12:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T14:05:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"502061ce68b32b42a2c154d4852713f86892d924","tid":384603,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"《國歌法》落實問題引起社會關注。立法會前主席曾鈺成認為，應對政府及立法會有信心。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成早上出席活動時表示，《國歌法》是簡單法例，而任何涉及刑事法例行為，都有準確和合適定義，不存在容易違法空間。他又說，市民應對政府和立法會有信心；若擔心會影響言論自由便應提出，相信政府會考慮。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成又說，不存在不覺意觸犯國歌法、好容易犯法的情況，指任何刑事行為有非常準確的定義，「一定有非常準確且合適定義，不存在不覺意犯了法&hellip;&hellip;甚至有些人話食麪包（聽到國歌）無站起來都犯法，完全是可笑的，對不對」。"},{"pid":"ba2ce1ace3d00f13ad82286ad1f0f4aa6ec479fb","tid":384603,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504326343115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504326343115&d=yMFP2zG%2F2ckRvWmh7XTl6DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=dfbdc888\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504326343115&h=2fa58607\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504326343115</a>"},{"pid":"e17f07f9ba11d66cc29f99fa3628f188f7681cfa","tid":384603,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"保皇狗：總之千錯萬錯都係市民錯，唔係政府錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898df474a86cb6335c45a16f0c6fc907bdd1b2f7","tid":384603,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保皇狗：總之千錯萬錯都係市民錯，唔係政府錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奶共狗:五毛狗，你們怕什麼?"},{"pid":"380daa7f4ccd62304e79a35f227d